{
  "stem": "23155.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they took first the very poor, and then the rich and the poor.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But by that time, Eichmann already had a plan to rid the whole of Europe of the Jews.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they had to start somewhere.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So they found a town by the name of Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It's named after the Empress Maria Theresa, or in Czech it's called Theresien, where they sent 1000 young men.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was called [NON-ENGLISH] to prepare the town for the rest of us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "This town was an armory, but it had a support group of people living there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "There were tailors, all the people who need to be in a town.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they had to find places where they were going to move because they wanted to empty [? out ?] the town And bring all the Jewish people from Bohemia and Moravia to Theresien.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So [NON-ENGLISH] prepared everything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They made cots and, of course, whatever needed to be done.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So the first transports started to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it usually was 1000 people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they would get a letter that they had to be in this and this place at this and this time and that they only could have one suitcase and things like that.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we were living there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was a very unsettling time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Even so, we were young, and you wanted to have other ideas about your future than going where we really didn't know.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Well, what did you want to be when you grew up?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Did you have special dreams?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I tell you, it's-- dreams-- at that time, people really couldn't have many dreams.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I did want to be an artist or perhaps someone who studied many languages because I have a very good ear for languages.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
